<table width="100%">
  <tr>
    <td class="content">
      <h3>Hello <%= fullname %>,</h3>
      <p>
        We're writing to let you know that your account connection to <strong><%= companyName %></strong>
        has been removed as of <%= disconnectedAt %>.
      </p>
      <p>
        Your roles at this organisation (<%= roles %>) have been revoked. You will no longer be able to
        access the platform under this account.
      </p>
      <p>
        If you believe this was done in error, please reach out to your account administrator directly.
      </p>
      <p>
        For further assistance, contact our support team:
        <a href="mailto:support@myproperty.com">Customer Support</a>
      </p>
    </td>
  </tr>
</table>
